lslink - List symbolic link chains
----------------------------------

  Like readlink -e, but lists each step of the way. For example:

    $ [mjhoy@nixos ~]$ lslink `which emacs`
    /nix/var/nix/profiles/default/bin/emacs
     /nix/store/i3vcbm0jh3cqylm37v472p0xhdniwy48-emacs-24.5/bin/emacs
     /nix/store/i3vcbm0jh3cqylm37v472p0xhdniwy48-emacs-24.5/bin/emacs-24.5

